/*
 * PERSISTENT DATA CONFIGURATION
 * =============================
 * 
 * ⚠️ IMPORTANT: Persistent directories cannot be configured in this file.
 * They must be configured through the CapRover Dashboard UI.
 * 
 * Required Setup Steps:
 * 1. Go to CapRover Dashboard: https://captain.indexo.ir/
 * 2. Select your backend app
 * 3. Go to App Configs → Persistent Directories
 * 4. Enable "Has Persistent Data"
 * 5. Add directory: /app/media
 * 6. Save & Update
 * 
 * See CAPROVER_PERSISTENT_SETUP.md for detailed instructions.
 * 
 * What gets persisted:
 * - /app/media/category_images/
 * - /app/media/subcategory_images/
 * - /app/media/product_images/
 * - /app/media/department_images/
 * - /app/media/blog_images/
 * - /app/media/user_images/
 */